)</i> in earlier centuries. Frequent in the medieval period, the name was revived in the 19th century, and has been especially popular in Scotland.  See also  Annis ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Agnes Grimston was born as the daughter of Roger Grimston. She married William Le Vavasour about 1309, in Denton, Yorkshire, England, United Kingdom. They were the parents of at least 2 sons."},"et":{"–":"Surnud","–Female":"Surnud","1287–Male":"1287–Surnud","1310–Male":"1310–Surnud","1329–Male":"1329–Surnud","–Male":"Surnud","about 1309":"umbes 1309","abt. 1329":"umbes 1329","1310":"1310","1287":"1287","about 1310":"umbes 1310","1329":"1329","of Denton, Yorksshire, England":"Denton, Yorkshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Denton, Yorks., Eng.":"Denton, Yorkshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","of Denton, Yorkshire, England":"Denton, Yorkshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"–":"Kuollut","–Female":"Kuollut","1287–Male":"1287–Kuollut","1310–Male":"1310–Kuollut","1329–Male":"1329–Kuollut","–Male":"Kuollut","about 1309":"noin 1309","abt. 1329":"noin 1329","1310":"1310","1287":"1287","about 1310":"noin 1310","1329":"1329","of Denton, Yorksshire, England":"Denton, Yorkshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Denton, Yorks., Eng.":"Denton, Yorkshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","of Denton, Yorkshire, England":"Denton, Yorkshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"–":"Décédée","–Female":"Décédée","1287–Male":"1287–Décédé","1310–Male":"1310–Décédé","1329–Male":"1329–Décédé","–Male":"Décédé","about 1309":"environ 1309","abt. 1329":"environ 1329","1310":"1310","1287":"1287","about 1310":"environ 1310","1329":"1329","of Denton, Yorksshire, England":"Denton, Everwyck, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Denton, Yorks., Eng.":"Denton, Everwyck, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","of Denton, Yorkshire, England":"Denton, Everwyck, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Agnes Grimston est née, fille de Roger Grimston. Elle a épousé William Le Vavasour environ 1309, à Denton, Everwyck, 